---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import ServicePage from '../templates/service/ServicePage.astro'
import ServiceSection from '../templates/service/ServiceSection.astro'
---

<ServicePage
  title="Senior Companionship Services | Maggi Maid Support in Bradford"
  description="Maggi Maid provides friendly companionship for seniors in Bradford—offering meaningful conversation, visits, and emotional support to ease loneliness."
>
  <Fragment slot="hero-image">
    <Image
      src={import('../assets/images/hero-image-1.png')}
      alt="A senior lady smiling and talking with her companion."
      loading="eager"
    />
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="heading">
    <span class="font-italic font-normal">Senior Companionship Services</span> in
    Bradford
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="hero-content">
    Whether you're looking for friendly company at home or someone to join you
    out in the community. My companionship services offer warm, attentive
    support for seniors who want to stay socially connected without the
    pressure. I understand how meaningful these connections are &mdash; and how
    anxiety or mobility issues can make them harder. My role isn't just to
    assist, but to help you enjoy these moments fully.
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="services">
    <ServiceSection
      id="home-sitting-service"
      number="01"
      heading="Home Sitting Service"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        Sometimes what's needed most is simply having someone there. I'll
        provide <span class="font-semibold"
          >calm, engaged company in your own home</span
        > &mdash; whether that means sharing stories over tea, helping with light
        hobbies, or just being present so you feel secure. Many families find this
        especially helpful when they can't visit as often as they'd like.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/light-domestic-cleaning-services.jpg')}
          alt="Light domestic cleaning services"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>

    <ServiceSection
      id="social-outings-and-trips"
      number="02"
      heading="Social Outings & Trips"
    >
      <Fragment slot="description">
        Staying connected shouldn't be difficult. My companionship and outing
        support for seniors helps you enjoy
        <span class="font-semibold">coffee meetups with friends</span>,
        <span class="font-semibold">local events</span>,
        <span class="font-semibold">park walks</span>,
        <span class="font-semibold">garden visits</span>, or
        <span class="font-semibold">religious services</span>—all with friendly,
        reliable assistance. Whether it's a weekly trip to the café, a community
        gathering, or simply getting out for fresh air, I provide patient,
        encouraging company so you can socialize with ease and joy.
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="image">
        <Image
          src={import('../assets/images/laundry-and-ironing-help.jpg')}
          alt="laundry and ironing help"
        />
      </Fragment>
    </ServiceSection>
  </Fragment>
</ServicePage>
